{"tid":1956171,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大風吹，吹咩風？","createTime":"2020-04-03T04:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T17:48:19.000Z","uid":125607,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb577422b702a4aa88219725b8a2957e94b965d","tid":1956171,"uid":125607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"「一早講過會大執架喎」、「人地翻新停業，吾遣散員工留黎一齊做翻新工人？定係你覺得啲員工應該全部停薪留職30個月更好？」、「其實一早已經講咗2020年會裝修 重裝後會改名麗晶酒店 全在計劃之內 大家唔使咁恐慌啦 唔好唯恐天下不亂啦！」、「間間公司都係咁㗎啦，有賠足仲想點」？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再攞兩三年前份新聞稿講話「洲際酒店2020年裝修打算2021重新以麗晶開業」嚟講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只有業界/洲際人先知酒店裝修呢壇嘢延期咗好多次，未宣布之前，酒店仍然賣緊2021年嘅客房 &amp; event space。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點：當年講到裝修嘅時候出哂email話全體同事仍會有薪有職，HR做哂功課詳細問每一個同事想喺裝修其間 reallocate 去邊 / 做咩部門 / cross training / 進修 etc，總之個個都有得繼續出糧，同事們就係因為呢個plan而繼續留低。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一場武漢肺炎，突然幫酒店光速地理直氣壯咁加快裝修嘅腳步。好多人覺得酒店好有良心咁賠足，仲想點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係，弱小一方的確無得可以點，但資方唔好營造到自己咁高貴。當另一間國際酒店龍頭連放no pay leave都可以有得俾員工揀plan A / plan B兼送回贈俾員工嘅時候，作為一個人性化嘅行業，所有嘢可以更有人性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPersonalized 呢樣嘢，可能只有酒店業先明。<br />\n如果唔明，麻煩don&rsquo;t blame the victim。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIHG Winning Ways:<br />\n#DoTheRightThing<br />\n#ShowWeCare<br />\n#AimHigher<br />\n#CelebrateDifference<br />\n#WorkBetterTogether"},{"pid":"b8a9f4b5906d1653b9d5ee0493178afbcccfba73","tid":1956171,"uid":182098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"所以唔明啲人成日話「賠足咪得囉」係咩心態🤷🏻&zwj;♂️🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n換轉果個係佢突然被炒<br />\n仲要經濟有排都未復甦無工作空缺<br />\n可以點捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e4792c9c7b114ce688da97ff5dd7bcf9d58dd8","tid":1956171,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成件事勁仆街呀"},{"pid":"f14791326509a6e31527b470d68af271cca31405","tid":1956171,"uid":49717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"推！！<br />\n真係好狗 我都係做酒店<br />\n如果比高層咁撚法我都唔忍"},{"pid":"bef26ea5dca187d42231e2b62073bbdc022eec04","tid":1956171,"uid":49717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58c19779b281cc46153d0dfda5ae13f4fe442be1","tid":1956171,"uid":58896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"身為酒店人絕對認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裝修根本就係炒人嘅藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896fc41b8ede934b099633acbefcee1553900c74","tid":1956171,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"最緊要正字 係唔<br />\n唔 唔 唔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce71a4bd4af89a34f432d9bd44de7ef3f507d11","tid":1956171,"uid":6181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"blame the victim 真係仆街<br />\n賠足代表佢冇咁賤啫, 唔代表佢依家唔賤囉<br />\n之前講到翻新果時都有糧出, 依家一野提早裝修就當員工condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n酒店都係黑心顧主黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8915a310d583a9c6a8df57a419dac9ba6788518f","tid":1956171,"uid":348731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"717b1387e15de2f62b8466af3cd84101600c33fe","tid":1956171,"uid":20339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"Posh"},{"pid":"0c7b5fb880f0db798ff2d52fbe8a398a534f2a33","tid":1956171,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:42:35.000Z","msg":"香港地真係冇乜良心顧主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c31f5f9f7134d4e30c825654d220a0de4e18b39","tid":1956171,"uid":88599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"dllm根本就係洲際借勢話提早裝修順便裁員慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6fda4679ff5aab1292be175be3b9fd8d78c392","tid":1956171,"uid":24124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"聽講佢地上幾個星期先sell人買佢地餐飲會藉，話下年二月先裝修⋯⋯<br />\n真係好仆街"},{"pid":"fe18b1f71e1e8340e4741608e3e8f7d3176a1a1f","tid":1956171,"uid":24124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e6fda4679ff5aab1292be175be3b9fd8d78c392","tid":1956171,"uid":24124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"聽講佢地上幾個星期先sell人買佢地餐飲會藉，話下年二月先裝修⋯⋯<br />\n真係好仆街"},"ci